            <title>[HBASE-17203] unable to see the namespaces and tables when grant read-only privleges</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-17203</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hi,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;i have created namespaces and given grant  read-only privileges. When i run &quot;list_namespace&quot; on hbase shell i am unable to see the namespaces and also the tables.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But namespaces and tables are able to see in HUE --&amp;gt; HBase browser.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Executed commands:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;create_namespace &apos;q1&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
grant &apos;@hadooptest&apos;,&apos;R&apos;,&apos;@q1&apos;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please advise.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
